{"tid":2185841,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"頂唔順屋企個老母","createTime":"2020-09-02T13:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T18:57:09.000Z","uid":243195,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d14ac97fcd75b3844ed6c1f295084dc41e0ff9c5","tid":2185841,"uid":243195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"叫春post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企個老母日日都鬧人 <br />\n由我味起身鬧到我訓教<br />\n呢排係屋企多 日日都比佢鬧真係覺得好辛苦<br />\n同佢講過好多次佢成日鬧人<br />\n次次講完都可以鬧番我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發脾氣又試過 唔理佢又試過 永遠都唔會理我  一係鬧番我轉頭 一係直情理都唔理我 <br />\n究竟呢個係咪我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前都唔會咁誇張<br />\n<br />\n每日係屋企都好撚辛苦 好撚想喊<br />\n好似得我一個想修補番個關係咁"},{"pid":"0bb297a451f859cbba4af87715a9d2c2f1ba1a67","tid":2185841,"uid":201414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"可如驗下血睇下你係咪佢親生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956d16403d092a292863ec5d6a3eab35e2ac5566","tid":2185841,"uid":243195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bb297a451f859cbba4af87715a9d2c2f1ba1a67","tid":2185841,"uid":201414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"可如驗下血睇下你係咪佢親生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:08:13.000Z","msg":"佢成日話我係執番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07331b71650641901c01bd629bc4cd7749b376a1","tid":2185841,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:09:29.000Z","msg":"出面個老母呢"},{"pid":"482cd019655d3b80a3cfe1760ffd06deea014a65","tid":2185841,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:09:54.000Z","msg":"做咩鬧你 鬧你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f0176c0f2ea813f437f478997e47d8c2acd556","tid":218584